OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be largely cloudy as
OL,6,Fbands of rain push northeast in the
OL,7,Fmorning. The rain will turn showery
OL,8,Flater, these showers heavy and
OL,9,Fthundery at times. Windy around the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowery rain clearing east at
OL,13,Ffirst. Then clear spells and a few
OL,14,Fshowers through the evening and
OL,15,Fovernight. Windy around the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FIt will stay largely dry
OL,18,Fwith bright or sunny spells but a few
OL,19,Fshowers possible from the west. Breezy
OL,20,Faround the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
