OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry Friday morning, then rain pushes
OL,7,Feast through the afternoon. Bright
OL,8,Fspells and showers on Saturday. Dry
OL,9,Fand bright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
